summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5412 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 24, Woodland Addition to Salmon Bay City, being the alley between North 46th Street and North 47th Street, from Fremont to Linden Avenue; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 67549, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
